OL,3,CUndertakers who left bodies to
OL,4,Cdecompose in unrefrigerated room to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FTwo funeral directors who allowed
OL,8,Fbodies to decompose in unrefrigerated
OL,9,Fconditions at their business in
OL,10,FGosport in Hampshire are due to be
OL,11,Fsentenced today.
OL,13,FIn December last year, Richard Elkin,
OL,14,F49, and Hayley Bell, 42, were both
OL,15,Ffound guilty at Portsmouth Crown Court
OL,16,Fof intentionally causing a public
OL,17,Fnuisance, preventing lawful burial,
OL,18,Fand carrying on business with intent
OL,19,Fto defraud creditors.
