OL,4,Cdecompose in unrefrigerated room to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FThe discovery was made when bailiffs,
OL,8,Fsent in by creditors, found two bodies
OL,9,Fstored in a room with water leaking
OL,10,Fthrough the ceiling.
OL,12,FOne had been left for 36 days and was
OL,13,Ffound in a badly decomposed condition.
OL,15,FHe was an elderly gentleman, whose
OL,16,Ffamily had arrived at a crematorium
OL,17,Fbelieving their loved one had been
OL,18,Fcremated to find out that in fact his
OL,19,Fbody remained at the funeral
OL,20,Fdirectors' premises.
