OL,3,CUndertakers who left bodies to
OL,4,Cdecompose in unrefrigerated room to be
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FFollowing a police investigation, it
OL,8,Fwas uncovered that between June 2022
OL,9,Fand December 2023, they kept the
OL,10,Fbodies in the unrefrigerated room,
OL,11,Fletting them decompose.
OL,13,FThey continued providing funeral
OL,14,Fservices despite knowing their
OL,15,Finsolvent business could not meet its
OL,16,Fobligations.
